{
  "stem": "13096.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And were all-- we were calling each other sister of-- of-- like you say, [ITALIAN].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Italian, it is [ITALIAN], like you say, bad luck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sister of bad luck, we used to call, you know, each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody what-- even after the camp, we meet them in Italy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were all called sisters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were all sisters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Did you see your father again after that one time that you mentioned?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- in the-- well, during the quarantine time, I been telling you, 40 days, the men were separated by the woman by this barbed wire, you know, electric barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we can see them every day for 40 days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why, you know, he was telling us all the advice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And many times, you know, when you were-- and then many times though we were three sisters and we needed that bread, I know my-- you know, my brothers, two brothers and my father were men, you know?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were used to eat more than we-- than the girl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes we were trying, you know, to save a piece of our-- of our ration.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were throwing over-- over the ones for them, to have them extra.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were having the same amount of, you know, piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we thought we can sacrifice ourselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were girls.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were not so-- I mean, we have good appetite, like, in normal time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the-- the boys, my brothers, they were 22, 24, just in the prime of their life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they used to have the best thing in Rhodes Island, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we were trying-- we were trying to help-- we were trying to help them, you know, to have a little bit, extra food.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
